    <item>
      <title>荷兰新任总理舒夫呼吁对华保持警惕</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/new-dutch-premier-schoof-calls-for-wary-approach-to-china</link>
      <description><![CDATA[荷兰新任首相迪克·绍夫表示，荷兰在与中国进行有关国家安全的讨论时必须“非常谨慎”，荷兰政府将面临有关敏感芯片制造设备出口的问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/new-dutch-premier-schoof-calls-for-wary-approach-to-china</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 13:12:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟监督机构称法国和意大利必须抓紧时间修复预算</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/france-and-italy-must-seize-day-to-fix-budgets-eu-watchdog-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟咨询监督机构敦促欧盟负债最多的国家控制支出，并削减官员认为过度扩张的赤字。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/france-and-italy-must-seize-day-to-fix-budgets-eu-watchdog-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 13:09:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>本届最高法院的赢家：特朗普、华尔街和保守派</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/supreme-court-s-term-recap-trump-wins-big-regulatory-landscape-altered</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国最高法院的保守主义革命又迎来了一次变革性的任期，共和党任命的绝对多数削减了监管者的权力，消除了唐纳德·特朗普竞选总统过程中的法律阴云，并为未来的重磅大案奠定了基础。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/supreme-court-s-term-recap-trump-wins-big-regulatory-landscape-altered</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 13:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>肯尼亚总统鲁托在抗议声中阻止公务员年度加薪</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/kenya-s-ruto-blocks-state-employee-annual-pay-rise-amid-protests</link>
      <description><![CDATA[肯尼亚总统威廉·鲁托要求国家财政部审查本月开始生效的公务员年度工资增长计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/kenya-s-ruto-blocks-state-employee-annual-pay-rise-amid-protests</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 12:45:53 GMT</pubDate>
